Package org.cloudbus.cloudsim.sdn

Class Switch

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.cloudbus.cloudsim.core.SimEntity
      • org.cloudbus.cloudsim.sdn.Switch
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.lang.Cloneable, Node
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    AggregationSwitch, CoreSwitch, EdgeSwitch
    public class Switch
extends SimEntity
implements Node
    This represents switches that maintain routing information. Note that all traffic estimation is calculated within NOS class, not in Switch class. Energy consumption of Switch is calculated in this class by utilization history.
    Since:
    CloudSimSDN 1.0
    Author:
    Jungmin Son, Rodrigo N. Calheiros
